🤔 Can't choose between retinol vs. retinal? Let us break it down!
.
Retinol is great for age prevention and addressing early signs of aging, like fine lines and wrinkles. TRY: Retinol Youth Renewal Serum
.
Retinal is ideal for treating advanced signs of aging, like deep-set wrinkles and sagging skin in need of a lift. TRY: Retinal ReSculpt Overnight Treatment
.
